description: This common Parvati purrs with a rating of 9, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 9, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Nine Lives for North, Box for East, Nine Lives for South, and Nine Lives for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Parvati [9 Votes, Common]
